<dl id="n12093c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12093c">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12093c"> 93(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 1.v. lay birchen bouquet / on sill</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Le 1<sub<ier</sub> mai, les jeunes gens qui courtisent une jeune fille vont la nuit poser sur ou pr&egrave;s de la fen&ecirc;tre la plus proche de son lit un &eacute;norme bouquet de bouleau orn&eacute; de fleurs. <br><font color="green">[On May Day the young men who court a girl go out at night and place on or close to the window closest to her bed an enormous bouquet of birch decorated with flowers.]</font> <small> Paul-Yves S&eacute;billot, <a name="RDTP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#RDTP"><cite title="source">Traditions et coutumes de Basse Bretagne</cite></a> (1904) 350</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
